{"tid":1463774,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"爭取外國輿論有助制裁","createTime":"2019-08-13T13:45:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:43:38.000Z","uid":157891,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"13399d31fb02d5f9aaeddd196cf3f474d3123531","tid":1463774,"uid":157891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:45:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1552018178269282&amp;id=416987405105704\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1552018178269282%26id%3D416987405105704&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2BqDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=8300fcc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1552018178269282&amp;id=416987405105704</a><br />\n<br />\n外媒反應點，絕對唔係冇影響，因為一但外媒都覺得示威錯，外國政要就唔會幫手制裁，港府就更加肆無忌憚鎮壓。<br />\n<br />\n香港經濟差中共係唔會擔心的，香港gdp只佔大陸咁少，而且珠三角仲有其他機場同港口可以用，只有香港商界會驚，但香港商界喺依件事上已經係完全冇影響力，中共只當佢地係棋子，係唔會考慮佢哋心情。中共驚的只有香港受到制裁令中共冇得再用香港調動資金。<br />\n<br />\n美國國會暑假後先會討論修訂香港政策法，如果期間外媒唔再幫示威，修訂可能都會凍過水。唔好忘記，長期關心香港民主的外國人永遠係少數，多數都係靠傳媒帶風向。比起本地民情轉向，國際民情轉向更大獲。<br />\n<br />\n唔係話唔好機場示威，或者唔好關閉機場，但要搞清楚，關閉機場係目標定手段？我個人嚟講，爭取外國關注係最大目標，而關注得嚟必須係同情示威者的。屌走晒外國支持絕對不利今場運動。要諗辦法點樣加強宣傳或微調做法，令關閉機場都繼續獲外媒同情"},{"pid":"9f5380fb2f1adda87bc461ceff460bfbc46254a6","tid":1463774,"uid":157891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:45:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"45350901409ef71b161ff5ed5a3c421a9fb24f47","tid":1463774,"uid":127309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:45:57.000Z","msg":"正是"},{"pid":"f5e741ac74559fc33168c03929d5ac61095b8be8","tid":1463774,"uid":49016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:46:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"186263b6c29c9af17b944eaea42687e433404f6b","tid":1463774,"uid":157891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:46:58.000Z","msg":"個人唔支持人手塞機場<br />\n希望各位睇吓思考吓"},{"pid":"77edb9a777856ff2f760dbac18bcd2c8ec030972","tid":1463774,"uid":74155,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:47:10.000Z","msg":"塞機場係為咗摙春袋<br />\n其他都係次要"},{"pid":"ee0aeb2208b15ee0552ac7de713a563ab8a1d272","tid":1463774,"uid":157891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:47:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c7f9d13dc1bde7a5bbd8240aadbd46f1ccdd90f","tid":1463774,"uid":175668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:47:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5cc6bc0ead66018a7c929a4a97c2fe6bd4e9d8aa","tid":1463774,"uid":127309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:48:00.000Z","msg":"如果好好睇睇 做足表面嘢 外國先幫得落手"},{"pid":"46d2902363385300405e52966bf661083748fe00","tid":1463774,"uid":161159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:48:31.000Z","msg":"所以請大家唔好互屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />心平氣和討論 <br />\n同樣為香港好嘅你地鬧黎鬧去我好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f83ed96518e3007135ca531658fefab6e46f79a","tid":1463774,"uid":157891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:50:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b5016408aa814ad8eca5cff594ee8d59d4734d47","tid":1463774,"uid":157891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:55:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"71a5cc72576daa2710679ce16372bb37b6970826","tid":1463774,"uid":86277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:58:09.000Z","msg":"可以叫外國人幫手寫信，要求佢地嘅政府介入<br />\n小弟寫咗少少idea請大家睇吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n推咗上國際頭版，跟住呢？【國際五大請求】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463264\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463264</a>"},{"pid":"bd73f584acbf315504f4bdca3496fdcf1cdcf239","tid":1463774,"uid":157891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:58:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e07fa8e12dd6d6d05b03e9a0f2bd4e614e8b17fc","tid":1463774,"ui